{"id":15635,"name":null,"username":"Mills","avatar_template":"/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/e480ec/{size}.png","created_at":"2020-05-10T10:01:39.000Z","cooked":"<p>Hello there, I dont know if there is still people here interested in this.</p>\n<p>Years ago I got some island models in 3DS format, from a project called LBANET. That project seems dead and I lost the copy I had downloaded.</p>\n<p>I found a program called lba2extviewer that can render all the 3d islands and it looks awesome. But there is no way to convert the models to a modern format.</p>\n<p>Id love to get the islands models to test an engine Im programming in C, or at least some info about the islands format to try and convert them myself.</p>\n<p>It would also be awesome to have lba2extviewer source.</p>\n<p>Thanks.</p>","post_number":1,"post_type":1,"posts_count":8,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T15:28:30.976Z","reply_count":4,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":13,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":85.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":15632,"topic_slug":"lba2-island-models","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"bookmarked":false,"raw":"Hello there, I don't know if there is still people here interested in this.\n\nYears ago I got some island models in 3DS format, from a project called LBANET. That project seems dead and I lost the copy I had downloaded.\n\nI found a program called lba2extviewer that can render all the 3d islands and it looks awesome. But there is no way to convert the models to a modern format.\n\nI'd love to get the islands models to test an engine I'm programming in C, or at least some info about the islands format to try and convert them myself.\n\nIt would also be awesome to have lba2extviewer source.\n\nThanks.","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":5557,"hidden":false,"trust_level":1,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba2-island-models/15632/1","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null,"can_vote":false}
